description: Living ink painting from foraged materials on paper to capture the soul of the Mountain West. Inks used are listed in the title. Through chemistry and alchemy, modifiers help shift the color as the ink dries. Created 2020, Minted April 2021 for OBJKT4OBJKT2. Measures 3000x3000 px. twitter @lilbridge, instagram bridgette_meinhold https://www.bridgettemeinhold.com/projects/living-ink-paintings
